\f4\b Pritha
\f2\b0 \
Pritha is mentioned in passing as Arjuna's mother.\
\

\f4\b Rama
\f2\b0 \
Rama was the son of Dasharatha and the king of Ayodha. He is famous for being the titular hero of the Ramayana, who slayed the demon Ravana to rescue his wife Sita.\
\

\f4\b Sanjaya
\f2\b0 \
Sanjaya is the wise sage who recounts the Gita epic to the blind king Dritarashtra, who cannot witness what is happening on the battlefield.\
\

\f4\b Shiva
\f2\b0 \
Shiva completes the "Trinity" of deities with Brahma and Vishnu -and is also known as the Destroyer.\
\

\f4\b Vishnu
\f2\b0 \
Vishnu is the Preserver, responsible for maintaining dharma in the world -and thus comes to the earth in various incarnations, to right the balance of good and evil.\
\

\f4\b Yudhishthira
\f2\b0 \
Arjuna's brother, and the rightful heir to the kingdom.\
